Body: Description: Hi Support, Hope this email finds you well. BDO is facing an issue with server storage, they are getting an alert on the server that their storage is nearly full. I request you to please check and free up storage as soon as possible. The server is hosted by Netwrix . URL : https://jiqh04r.hosted.endpointprotector.com/index.php Please find attached screenshot. Should you require any more details, please let me know. Thanks, Milan Singh

What We've Learned Updated: 05-05 The customer BDO Malaysia encounter an issue with their disk usage.
They are hosted in our environment.

06-05 We have cleared the disk usage after we have requested access to their backend.

Next Steps Updated: 05-05 We have requested access to their backend.

06-05 We will close the case.
